title: Brooch and box
description: Brooch composed of seed pearls in a design of central ornament with six radiating scrolls; metal pin and plate on back.  Box covered in black leather; lined with dark blue velvet and pale blue satin printed with "Tiffany and Co. 550 Broadway New York" in gold letters.
